1
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:42,220
Brother Li,

2
00:00:42,360 --> 00:00:42,760
you...

3
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:49,040
I am Lanqi Moyuan.

4
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,280
So pretentious?

5
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:51,920
We didn't mean

6
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:53,320
to offend the Demon Lord.

7
00:00:53,480 --> 00:00:54,480
Please, Demon...

8
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:56,520
Danyu,

9
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:58,120
why aren't you

10
00:00:58,120 --> 00:00:59,120
surprised at all?

11
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:00,880
Did you already know?

12
00:01:02,720 --> 00:01:04,000
I didn't know.

13
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:05,379
If you didn't know,

14
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,260
why do you have no reaction at all?

15
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:10,280
I'm so scared.

16
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:11,880
Demon King, please don't eat me.

17
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:13,240
Please don't eat me.

18
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,140
Demon Lord,

19
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,120
please allow

20
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:20,800
us to leave.

21
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,289
Get lost.

22
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:28,920
Danyu,

23
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,320
what are you waiting for?

24
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:30,880
Let's go.

25
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:31,760
Okay.

26
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,880
Qinglan, oh, Qinglan.

27
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:52,039
Your bloodline has been lost outside for 20 years.

28
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:56,200
It is time for it to return.

29
00:01:57,960 --> 00:02:00,800
The great cause of Tiandao Palace

30
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:06,800
needs the backing of your Likong Clan.

31
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,400
Danyu.

32
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,440
I will take Wuzhou to heal his wounds first.

33
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,300
In this battle,

34
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,690
everyone is exhausted.

35
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,880
You are injured too.

36
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:33,320
Hurry back to your room and rest.

37
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,520
After I settle Wuzhou down,

38
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:36,120
I'll come back and treat you.

39
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:38,640
Don't worry about me, Sister Mu.

40
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:41,300
Brother Wuzhou's injuries are more important.

41
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:42,680
Wuzhou.

42
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,800
This demon king is quite handsome.

43
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:10,880
What a pity.

44
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,760
I will be able to complete the mission soon.

45
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,290
I'll be able to go home soon.

46
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:19,860
Thank you both for taking me in and caring for me.

47
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,400
Especially

48
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:23,880
Miss Lu, who found me in deep trouble.

49
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,200
What?

50
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,360
He is in

51
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,440
your room.

52
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,040
No.

53
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:35,680
He...

54
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,960
I admire him.

55
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,440
I definitely didn't kiss you

56
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,360
just because of your beauty.

57
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:56,660
This is bad.

58
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,840
The Child of the World is in danger.

59
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,720
I got it.

60
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,279
You saved us,

61
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:20,560
so you are our benefactor.

62
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,490
Thanking you is the least we can do.

63
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,560
Is that so?

64
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:26,770
Then remember this.

65
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,160
Your life

66
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:29,760
is mine now.

67
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,600
Consider this little bit of blood

68
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,520
as interest.

69
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,360
This Likong Clan

70
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,880
is particularly resistant.

71
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:04,880
What should we do?

72
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:08,320
Take her back.

73
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,930
Don't be afraid to hurt her.

74
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:11,420
As long as she doesn't die.

75
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:38,120
Lu Danyu.

76
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:40,340
I shouldn't have to sleep for now.

77
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,159
Yiyi.

78
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,700
You've recovered.

79
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:47,320
The origin power of the previous Child of the World has returned.

80
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,320
With the increase of the origin,

81
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,520
I have enough energy,

82
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,520
so I don't have to keep sleeping.

83
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,520
Great.

84
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,380
Fighting alone is really too difficult.

85
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,720
The people of Tiandao Palace have found the demon.

86
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:01,200
As long as you and the Daughter of the World stay away from him

87
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:03,360
and don't let him find a chance to sacrifice you to heaven,

88
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:05,920
he shouldn't have enough ability to destroy the world.

89
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,200
If it cannot be avoided,

90
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:09,860
you can also rely on the power of Tiandao Palace.

91
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,400
Yiyi.

92
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:12,840
You all say

93
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,240
that Tiandao Palace is the leader of the human race,

94
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,520
maintaining fairness and justice for humans.

95
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,440
But today,

96
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:19,800
for the first time,

97
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,060
facing them directly,

98
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,880
they made me feel very bad.

99
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,520
Feel?

100
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,600
Yiyi.

101
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,160
Do you know that Lanqi Moyuan

102
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:31,090
once suppressed the Netherworld for the human race?

103
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,040
I know.

104
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,040
If you knew, why didn't you tell me?

105
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,970
Is it important?

106
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,760
Of course it is.

107
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,240
The contrast is huge.

108
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:40,920
From a human hero

109
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,440
to a demon king destroying the world.

110
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:44,240
God knows what he's been through

111
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,800
to make him like this.

112
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:47,570
Experience?

113
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:48,480
You mean

114
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,600
his life path?

115
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:50,520
Right.

116
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:52,640
Something important

117
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:54,100
must have changed him.

118
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:57,640
For the world's operation, his life path

119
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:59,760
is one of countless similar paths.

120
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,860
It happens every day in the world.

121
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,520
But no one is like him,

122
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:04,780
destroying the world.

123
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:06,900
I can't extract useful information.

124
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,290
That's true.

125
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:11,040
Yiyi can't perceive human emotions.

126
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,720
I'm afraid it's hard for you to understand

127
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,980
the cause and effect driven by emotions.

128
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,940
No wonder after so many loops,

129
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:19,400
the ending is still the destruction of the world.

130
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:21,440
With such an unchanging path,

131
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:23,200
no matter how many times you walk it,

132
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,730
the result will be the same.

133
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,120
Yiyi.

134
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,680
I can't listen to you on this matter.

135
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,409
I'm going to find Lanqi Moyuan.

136
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:34,960
I want to know

137
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,960
why he wants to destroy the world.

138
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:37,680
Lu Danyu,

139
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,460
you'll be in great danger.

140
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:41,960
Yiyi,

141
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,520
he won't hurt me.

142
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,240
Danyu,

143
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,920
my injuries are almost healed.

144
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,580
How are you?

145
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,520
Do you want Xiaoxue to heal your injuries?

146
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:01,360
Yes, Danyu.

147
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:03,200
I can heal you now.

148
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:09,160
Danyu.

149
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,920
Danyu, are you there?

150
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,720
Danyu,

151
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,040
say something.

152
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,720
Danyu!

153
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:14,840
Danyu!

154
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,570
Why is there no sound at all?

155
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:19,440
Could something have happened?

156
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,280
Brother Wuzhou,

157
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:29,000
Sister Mu,

158
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:31,940
I don't think Lanqi Moyuan is a murderous fiend.

159
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,690
I'm going to find out the truth.

160
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,159
Lu Danyu,

161
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,120
you're being too reckless.
